The '''William J. Jameson Law Library''' is the library of the [[Alexander Blewett&nbsp;III School of Law]] at the [[University of Montana]] in [[Missoula, Montana|Missoula]]. It is {{convert|20060|sqft|m2}} in size<ref name="selfstudy">{{cite web |url=http://www.umt.edu/self-study2010/std5/std5exhibits/RE5-06LawLibraryself-study2009.docx |title=Self-Study Report: Law Library |publisher=Alexander Blewett&nbsp;III School of Law at the University of Montana |work=University of Montana Law Library Self Study |date=2009-11-04 |page=4 |format=DOC}}</ref> and is the only academic law library in the state of Montana.<ref name="selfstudy"/>

